 4332, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Edwards scored 13 off the bench.\", \"from\": 4333, \"to\": 4365, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jayson Tatum (eight points) had some strong drives to the rim.\", \"from\": 4366, \"to\": 4428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4366, \"end\": 4378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jayson_Tatum\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jayson Tatum\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jayson_Tatum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jayson_Tatum\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Team USA\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s all-time leading scorer (Kevin Durant, who is resting a minor calf injury) watched the game in street clothes.\\u00c2  There are things to clean up, sure.\", \"from\": 4429, \"to\": 4601, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4484, \"end\": 4490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2005234863456013e-29, \"text\": \"Durant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But no reason to believe they won\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t.\\u00c2  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve got to coach them,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Kerr said.\", \"from\": 4602, \"to\": 4685, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThey have got to get better, they know that.\", \"from\": 4686, \"to\": 4733, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have got to get better as a staff.\", \"from\": 4734, \"to\": 4771, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Every day we are focused on that.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\\u00c2  Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 4772, \"to\": 4837, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations  Chris Mannix is a senior writer at Sports Illustrated covering the NBA and boxin